---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import statsLanding from '../../../assets/photos/formazione1.webp';
import chatResults from '../../../assets/photos/formazione2.webp';
import adCreativa from '../../../assets/photos/formazione3.webp';

const calendlyUrl = 'https://calendly.com/davideveneto/caffe-strategico';
---

<Layout
	lang="en"
	title="ROAS 4x — Training course sold at double the price | Davide Veneto"
	description="How we sold a training course at double the competitors' price with a 4x return on every euro invested."
>
	<section class="pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-28 relative">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<a href="/en/" class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-[0.2em] mb-6 inline-block hover:text-red-glow transition-colors">&larr; BACK TO HOME</a>
			<p class="text-red font-heading text-lg tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">TRAINING</p>
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading leading-[0.95] mb-6">
				4x return<br />
				<span class="text-red">for every 1 invested</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-gray-300 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
				How we sold a training course at double the competitors' price, generating a 4x ROAS.
			</p>
			<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-red mt-8"></div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-black-light border-t border-b border-white/5">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">The context</h2>
			<div class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
				<p>The client sells a mandatory training course for dental assistants. The course is required and the target audience is used to taking it online for 50-60 each.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-8">
				<div class="p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-wider mb-2">PRODUCT</p>
					<p class="text-white font-semibold">In-person, at roughly double the price</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-wider mb-2">MARKET</p>
					<p class="text-white font-semibold">"Standard" offer, same old topics</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-wider mb-2">UNIQUE ANGLE</p>
					<p class="text-white font-semibold">The next step: managerial training</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="section-divider mb-8"></div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">Target <span class="text-red">analysis</span></h2>
			<div class="p-6 bg-black-card border border-red/20">
				<p class="text-white text-lg leading-relaxed">Mostly young women who feel they can give more, but don't feel valued. I discovered this from the answers they gave when joining the client's free Facebook group.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-black-light border-t border-b border-white/5">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="section-divider mb-8"></div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">The <span class="text-red">strategy</span></h2>
			<div class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
				<p class="text-white font-semibold">How did we differentiate?</p>
				<p>I told my client to include managerial training content in the mandatory course, to differentiate it and leverage the dissatisfaction and repetitiveness of competitors' courses.</p>
				<div class="grid gap-4 mt-6">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
						<span class="text-red font-heading text-2xl">01</span>
						<p class="text-gray-300">I wrote and built the landing page</p>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
						<span class="text-red font-heading text-2xl">02</span>
						<p class="text-gray-300">I created ads on Facebook and Instagram</p>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
						<span class="text-red font-heading text-2xl">03</span>
						<p class="text-gray-300">We spend about 50/day and get 2 contacts. 90% of these contacts ask questions to a consultant and sign up for the course.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="section-divider mb-8 mx-auto text-center"></div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8 text-center">The <span class="text-red">results</span></h2>
			<div class="p-8 bg-red/10 border border-red/30 text-center mb-8">
				<p class="text-red font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-4">ROAS 4x</p>
				<p class="text-white text-xl">Every euro invested generated 4 in revenue. Upsells were offered during the in-person session.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
				<div>
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-wider mb-3">LANDING PAGE STATS</p>
					<img src={(statsLanding as any).src ?? statsLanding} alt="Landing page statistics" class="w-full rounded border border-gray-700/50" />
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-wider mb-3">REAL RESULTS</p>
					<img src={(chatResults as any).src ?? chatResults} alt="WhatsApp chat with sales results" class="w-full rounded border border-gray-700/50" />
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mt-8">
				<p class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-wider mb-3">TOP PERFORMING CREATIVE</p>
				<img src={(adCreativa as any).src ?? adCreativa} alt="Course ads creative" class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto rounded border border-gray-700/50" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-24 md:py-40 bg-red relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative">
			<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-white/30 mb-8 mx-auto"></div>
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading mb-6 text-white">Want similar results<br />for your business?</h2>
			<p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-10">Book a free 30-minute call. Let's analyze your situation together.</p>
			<a href={calendlyUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary-inverted">Book a strategy call</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<footer class="py-8 border-t border-gray-700/30">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
			<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Power Adv di Veneto Davide. All rights reserved.</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
</Layout>
